node.text:
A new Poorly Drawn Lines animated series is coming to Cake on FXX! Starring @tonyrevolori @darcycarden and @ronfunch , episodes start airing Sept 30 on FXX and the next day on FX on Hulu. ⁣
⁣
“Based on Reza Farazmand’s comic of the same name, Poorly Drawn Lines spotlights the fantastical misadventures of Ernesto (Tony Revolori), Tanya (D'Arcy Carden) and Kevin (Ron Funches)—three twenty-something best friends navigating early adulthood in a world where the strange and surreal are an everyday thing. It will air within season five of FXX’s Cake, a carefully curated, half-hour weekly showcase featuring both live-action and animated comedy programs of varied lengths from a diverse array of storytellers.”
